    <sect3 role="package">
      <title>Introduo a Doxyqml Module</title>

      <para>
        The <application>Doxyqml</application> package allows using Doxygen to
document QML classes.
      </para>

      &lfs113_checked;

      <bridgehead renderas="sect4">Informao do Pacote</bridgehead>
      <itemizedlist spacing="compact">
        <listitem>
          <para>
            Transferncia (HTTP): <ulink url="&doxyqml-download-http;"/>
          </para>
        </listitem>
        <listitem>
          <para>
            Transferncia (FTP): <ulink url="&doxyqml-download-ftp;"/>
          </para>
        </listitem>
        <listitem>
          <para>
            Soma de verificao MD5: &doxyqml-md5sum;
          </para>
        </listitem>
        <listitem>
          <para>
            Tamanho da transferncia: &doxyqml-size;
          </para>
        </listitem>
        <listitem>
          <para>
            Espao em disco estimado exigido: &doxyqml-buildsize;
          </para>
        </listitem>
        <listitem>
          <para>
            Tempo de construo estimado: &doxyqml-time;
          </para>
        </listitem>
      </itemizedlist>

      <bridgehead renderas="sect4">Dependncias de Doxyqml</bridgehead>

      <bridgehead renderas="sect5">Required (Run Time)</bridgehead>
      <para role="required">
        <xref role="runtime" linkend="doxygen"/>
      </para>

      <bridgehead renderas="sect5">Optional (for testing)</bridgehead>
      <para role="optional">
        <xref linkend="pytest"/>
      </para>

    </sect3>

    <sect3 role="installation">
      <title>Instalao de Doxyqml</title>

    <para> Build the module: </para>

<screen><userinput>pip3 wheel -w dist --no-build-isolation --no-deps $PWD</userinput></screen>

    <para>
      Agora, como o(a) usurio(a) <systemitem class="username">root</systemitem>:
    </para>

<screen role="root"><userinput>pip3 install --no-index --find-links dist --no-cache-dir --no-user doxyqml</userinput></screen>

    <para>
      To test the installation, run:
    </para>

<screen remap="test"><userinput>pytest</userinput></screen>

    <para>
      The <emphasis>test_qmlclass.py</emphasis> test is known to fail.
    </para>

    </sect3>

